      <title>“已到极限”：墨西哥电网瘫痪威胁近岸外包</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/-at-its-limit-mexico-s-buckling-grid-threatens-nearshoring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蓬勃发展的经济和极端的气温使墨西哥各地的电网濒临崩溃，而随着每个新的工业园区和仓库的建立，危机变得更加严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/-at-its-limit-mexico-s-buckling-grid-threatens-nearshoring</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
